            </p>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Şirketler Hukuku</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                        <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="mr-2">•</span>
